Removing trials without response (> 1500 ms) or EMG onset.

In [4]:
data = data[(data.trialType != 'NR') & (data.trialType != 'UT')].reset_index(drop=True)#Removing unmarked EMG trials

Applying and visualizing EWMA cut-offs¶

In [5]:
for sub, subdat in data.groupby(['participant','condition']):#Condition = SAT
    print(sub)
    cutoff = ewmaseg(subdat.response.values, subdat.rt.values, alpha=.02, limit=.6, plotit=True)['rtbound']
    data.drop(subdat[subdat.rt < cutoff].index, inplace =True, axis=0)
    plt.show()
